Let me dwell briefly on the procedure involved; on my inability tofollow it consciously in my mind--my unwieldy and disobedient mind! In orderto make myself imagine the pivotal process I have to force an oppositerevolution of the decor: I must try, dear friend and assistant, to swing theentire length of the street, with the massive fa–≥ades of its houses beforeand behind me